How does it work?
==================

- Each write is written to 6 independent location across the region
- 4 confirmed writes acknowlege successfully
- Repair the corrupted using aother node


Performance:
============
    - Postgres is 2 -3 times faster than normal
    - MySQL is 5 times faster
    - better at scale
    - Take it with a grain of salt

Storage is 64 TB
Continuous backup to S3


Provision a Aurora Postgres Cluster:
====================================

    - Provision a Postgres Aurora Cluster
    - Enable Multi AZ
    - Connect to different endpoints
    - Validate Reader Enpoints
    